					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Sonya Lea</h4>
												<p>Sonya Lea is the author of the memoir <em>Wondering Who You Are</em>, which garnered praise from <em>Oprah Magazine</em>, <em>People</em>, and the BBC. She teaches at workshops and creates writing retreats in the US and Canada. Her essays have appeared in <em>Salon</em>, <em>Southern Review</em>, <em>Guernica</em>, <em>Los Angeles Review of Books</em>, and <em>Ms.</em> magazine, among others.</p>
					</div>
